<TD ALIGN="LEFT">double</TD>
<TD ALIGN="LEFT">The analog signal to be digitized if interleave mode is selected. Note: For simulation only.</TD>
</TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="LEFT"><SPAN  CLASS="textit">sim_i</SPAN></TD>
<TD ALIGN="LEFT">in</TD>
<TD ALIGN="LEFT">double</TD>
